Interface HangMan

All Known Implementing Classes:
Game, User
public interface HangMan

This Interface defines the methods that will be used to gather information from the User to set up the rules of the HangMan Game

Version:
(September 18, 2012 : Windows Vista(x32)
Author:
(Jesse Nelson)
